description: "Maritime map of the Philippines, with inset maps of bays showing bathymetry (sea depth), shoals, reefs and anchor points. There is also an inset map of Taal Volcano, and elevations (side views of terrestrial landmarks like mountains and islands)."
title: "Reduzirte   Karte   von   den   Philippinen   und   den   Sulu   Inseln"
